BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 223.2 750 Td (UNDERSTANDING IEP GOALS) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 715 Td (An IEP \(Individualized Education Program\) is a legal document that) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 698 Td (outlines your child's educational goals and the support they'll receive.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 681 Td (Understanding how goals work empowers you as a parent advocate.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 664 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 647 Td (SMART GOALS FORMAT:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 630 Td (S - Specific: What exactly will the child do?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 613 Td (M - Measurable: How will progress be tracked? \(numbers, percentages\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 596 Td (A - Achievable: Is this realistic for your child?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 579 Td (R - Relevant: Does this address a real need?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 562 Td (T - Time-bound: By when? \(usually within the IEP year\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 545 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 528 Td (EXAMPLE OF A GOOD IEP GOAL:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 511 Td ('By [date], [child] will read grade-level passages and answer) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 494 Td (comprehension questions with 80% accuracy in 4 out of 5 trials,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 477 Td (as measured by teacher-created assessments.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 460 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 443 Td (WHAT TO LOOK FOR IN YOUR CHILD'S GOALS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 426 Td (- Is the baseline stated? \(where they are NOW\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 409 Td (- Is the target clear? \(where they should be\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 392 Td (- How will it be measured? \(data collection method\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 375 Td (- How often will data be collected?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 358 Td (- Is progress reported to you regularly?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 341 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 324 Td (YOUR ROLE AS A PARENT:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 307 Td (- Request progress reports \(at least quarterly\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 290 Td (- Track progress at home \(this workbook helps!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 273 Td (- Attend all IEP meetings prepared) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 256 Td (- Ask questions when goals are unclear) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10.5 Tf 50 239 Td (- Request changes if goals aren't appropriate) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
